title: Second Date Update: Abandoned Children's Hospital
itunes:title: Second Date Update: Abandoned Children's Hospital
description: If your date said to you "Hey, wanna go to an abandoned building where I heard some people died?” most people would run, but our listener actually WENT...And believe it or not, that still wasn't the strangest thing he said to her that night.
